# ShopMate UI Design Guidelines

## Color Scheme

- **Primary Color**: `@color/primary` (#FF6B35) - Main brand color
- **Secondary Color**: `@color/secondary` (#6366F1) - Accent color
- **Background**: `@color/background` (#F8FAFC) - Light background
- **Card Background**: `@color/card_background` (#FFFFFF) - White card surfaces
- **Text Primary**: `@color/text_primary` (#0F172A) - Main text color
- **Text Secondary**: `@color/text_secondary` (#475569) - Secondary text color

## Components

- Use `MaterialCardView` for card containers with `app:cardCornerRadius="16dp"`
- Use `MaterialButton` for primary actions with `app:cornerRadius="12dp"`
- Use `TextInputLayout` with `style="@style/Widget.MaterialComponents.TextInputLayout.OutlinedBox"`
- Set `android:textAllCaps="false"` on buttons for modern style

## Spacing

- Standard margin between elements: 16dp
- Card padding: 24dp
- Standard button height: 56dp
